tag_message: Crash fix when mailing from external app
Various improvements from K-9 up to version 4.904
Setting subtype for plain text messages
PGP inline sig verification for non-Western charsets
Ensure proper line endings to quoted text
Support for receipt of PGP/MIME messages
Support for integrated decryption of attachments
